Installation instructions
=========================

Compile Instructions
  - Assumption: INDI package installed (see https://indilib.org/download.html)
  - Retrieve the sources for the Herkules-driver
    git clone https://github.com/escribana/indi-3rdparty.git
  - cd indi-3rdparty
    checkout branch "master"
  - mkdir -p build/indi_herkules
  - cd build/indi_herkules
  - cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ../../indi_herkules
  - sudo make install

And now start the INDI server and kstars.

